  "title": "Assistant Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description </strong></p><p> Appraise building plan submission for Sewerage/Drainage</p><p>works and Water Service Notification/TOP/CSC applications</p><p>according to standards (e.g., COP and requirements</p><p>stipulated by the Board).</p><p> To consult and co-ordinate with the Departments within PUB</p><p>to process submissions according to statutory legislation,</p><p>standards and requirements as stipulated by the Board (e.g.,</p><p>processing of new water connections, A/A works, etc.)</p><p> To prepare submission report to record the number of</p><p>submissions reviewed.</p><p> To consider developing methods to automate the submission</p><p>reviews.</p><p> To conduct any other works in relation to the submissions as</p><p>required by the Board.</p>",
